                                                                                            <p>A predictive dialer is an outbound call center solution. It used a mathematical formula to predict the agent&#8217;s availability time. Furthermore, dials multiple calls for one agent but connects only the productive calls. Besides, it auto-drops voicemail, unanswered, unproductive calls instantly.</p>
