                                                                                        <div id="elementor-tab-content-5332" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-5332">
                                                                                            <p>Predictive dialer focuses on the productivity of the agents. It uses algorithms to predict both the average call answer time and agent availability. Additionally, it auto-dials multiple calls for each agent and routes answered calls to them. The software also ignores unanswered, busy, and disconnected numbers. You can now automate all your campaigns and focus all your resources into getting promising leads.</p>
